name: CWO Photo
author: Creaweb

sections.description:
After login with Google and creating Google credentials in Google console developers, you will have access to your own Google Photos albums. Using shortcodes, you will be able to display your photos anywhere on your website. You can add several parameters in the shortcode in order to customize it and then obtain the result you want.

Arbitrary section 1
sections.installation:
1. Unzip “cwo_photo.zip” to the /wp-content/plugins/ directory
  2. Activate the plugin through the ‘Plugins’ menu in WordPress
sections.faq:
Where can I find installation and configuration informations ?

How to create my own Google credentials ?

How to use shortcodes in order to customize and display my photos ?

For more information, please go on our website https://cwo-photo.com
sections.changelog:
V 0.1 : initial release
V 1.0 : first non beta version
